title: Where in the world is The News-Reporter…
text: The News-Reporter traveled with Ginny King and Skeet Willingham to Beverly Hills, California, this week in celebration of Ginny’s birthday. As part of their trip, they attended the Rose Bowl game between the Oregon Ducks and the Wisconsin Badgers. This News-Reporter is 2,039 miles from home.
